Na kolanda zulunalo South China Morning Post, Shinzo Abe atindelaki bakonzi ya Trump mokanda mpo na kosomba nkisi yango, oyo ekoki kozala na nguya moke na bato oyo babɛlaka yango makasi, epai virisi yango ezali naino kopalangana.
